ohc=fRfPiDd0RGEQ7kNvgEQTvjV&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCLTRBzJ4N7djTEBWIf8pKsXDd8kz5czDOGLNAxONuyQQ&oe=6756DF94"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "246754393025091", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/11162788_1159088237569028_8479258378613293056_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=MQkQZMMyqKwQ7kNvgE7or8Q&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD1o57XVPsH-cwcAof-2UNZnBCGENYbbx25S5RSLxFrCA&oe=6756C466"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Raising A Rukus", "keywords": ["Animated", "Kids", "Dog", "Dinosaur", "Film"], "long_description": "This adventure requires 2.6 GB total.\n\nTwins Amy and Jonas just found a dog- or did he find them? Either way, Rukus has a magical secret \u2013 he\u2019s about to take them to a whole new world. \n\nEqual parts thrilling, breathtaking, and inspiring, Raising a Rukus is an animated adventure like no other. With cutting edge \u201cbranching narratives,\u201d choose which character\u2019s journey you want to follow by a simple gaze with your eyes. \n\nJump right into magical, rollercoaster journey through a prehistoric world! Come along for the ride with Jonas and Amy as the river propels you, dinosaurs chase you, and Rukus delights you!\n\nRaising a Rukus is the first episode of the groundbreaking new franchise from the Academy Award Winning Production Designer of Avatar and the Director of Maleficent.", "short_description": "This adventure requires 2.6 GB total.\n\nRide along with twins Amy and Jonas as they chase their mischievous pet dog, Rukus, through an amazing adventure into a prehistoric world. \n\nWith cutting edge \u201cbranching narratives,\u201d choose which character to follow and discover a different path with a simple gaze of your eyes!\n\nA new animated experience from Oscar-winner Robert Stromberg and The Virtual Reality Company."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "h